<A>__{butch walks underneath the tree without even looking at phillip. he sits down to rest.}
<C>__{butch}
<D>__{alaska, phillip. wild and wooley. man against nature. me personally, i like them odds.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{did i tell you my daddy lives there? he's the one that sent the picture postcard. listen here to what he says about it...}
